The standard error message for converting/rendering issues with the Office Connector is:

{quote}There was a problem converting this attachment. Please create an issue at http://jira.atlassian.com{quote}

However since we tend to investigate potential bugs through http://support.atlassian.com first this is confusing. We should update the error message to http://support.atlassian.com first, and then create a bug report if necessary.

